===Noun===
#A sacred act in [[Christianity]] that is done to [[consecrate]] oneself to [[God]].  

The Roman Catholic and Eastern churches list seven sacraments:
# [[baptism]]
# [[confirmation]]
# [[communion]], (or [[Mass]] or [[Eucharist]]) 
# [[penance]]
# [[extreme unction]]
# [[holy orders]]
# [[matrimony]]

